Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.27,0:00:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子长大的主妇们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该找点事情来做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日子才过得有意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生才会过得充实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.46,0:00:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有兴趣的人生很无味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得毫无意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣这种东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.48,0:00:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个年纪再学新的东西很困难呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.82,0:00:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是想尝试一些新的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣 主妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.84,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,cosplay ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.35,0:01:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到cosplay
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.69,0:01:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到的就是年轻人玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.86,0:01:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回是主妇玩cosplay
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.03,0:01:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我推荐主妇玩cosplay
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.21,0:01:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主妇很擅长这个的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.88,0:01:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己做的cosplay会更有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.06,0:01:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 被他人看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.23,0:01:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以保持女性的美丽\N是非常不错的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错呀 cosplay
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.09,0:02:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友的妈妈玩cosplay
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.95,0:02:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 用这些针线做些可爱的\Ncosplay服装吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这么华丽的衣服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秘密 不能说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了也会让你看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去打工了\N慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.54,0:03:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤一直喜欢拍照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来成为摄影师是我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明 欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈你这是什么装扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是cosplay\N合适吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤 好久不见\N你觉得怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.64,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很合适你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.81,0:05:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思\N打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.51,0:05:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一页好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.18,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一也很值得拍照呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也不错哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有听我说话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在听呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思\N我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在马上去\N抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.91,0:06:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工那里叫我过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N你先自己玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好在意小明的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.86,0:08:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明打工那边有重要的事出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明真是的\N朋友好不容易来玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.73,0:08:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么在发呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.91,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想让你帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.76,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.93,0:08:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易玩一次Cosplay
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想让你帮我拍些照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤是摄影部的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍照片吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.94,0:09:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己一个人拍不了的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到小明回来就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤\N不可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
